data.text:
The City of Enterprise is committed to providing quality customer service and is the providing link between the public and the Elected/Appointed Officials for the City of Enterprise.

Administrative/Executive meetings are scheduled for the fourth Thursday of every month at 7:00am.

This is public meeting and takes place at the Enterprise City Hall. For more information pertaining to the Administrative/Executive meetings, please contact Lacey McQuead via lmcquead [at] enterpriseoregon.gov (Email).

Office hours are 8:00am-4:00pm Monday through Thursday and Friday by appointment only.

If you would like to schedule an appointment, please contact Gina Birkmaier at 541-426-4196.
